plot: Cocksure bailiff, Duncan, enjoys his job and he is good at it, until he meets Anna. She's a debtor of a different stripe, not in the least intimidated by his boorish tactics. When Duncan finds himself falling for her he risks exposing himself to rejection.
title: Au Revoir Monkeys
